{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":980,"text":"There's a man by the name of Captain"},{"time":3240,"text":"William Swenson"},{"time":5570,"text":"who recently was awarded the\ncongressional Medal of Honor"},{"time":8772,"text":"for his actions on September 8, 2009."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13630,"text":"On that day, a column of American"},{"time":15995,"text":"and Afghan troops"},{"time":17279,"text":"were making their way"},{"time":18756,"text":"through a part of Afghanistan"},{"time":21640,"text":"to help protect"},{"time":24913,"text":"a group of government officials,"},{"time":26008,"text":"a group of Afghan government officials,"},{"time":27854,"text":"who would be meeting with some local"},{"time":30220,"text":"village elders."},{"time":31723,"text":"The column came under ambush,"},{"time":33990,"text":"and was surrounded on three sides,"},{"time":36497,"text":"and amongst many other things,"},{"time":39437,"text":"Captain Swenson was recognized"},{"time":40843,"text":"for running into live fire"},{"time":43060,"text":"to rescue the wounded"},{"time":44241,"text":"and pull out the dead."},{"time":48464,"text":"One of the people he rescued was a sergeant,"},{"time":51320,"text":"and he and a comrade were making their way"},{"time":53758,"text":"to a medevac helicopter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56048,"text":"And what was remarkable about this day"},{"time":58236,"text":"is, by sheer coincidence,"},{"time":60227,"text":"one of the medevac medics"},{"time":61907,"text":"happened to have a GoPro camera on his helmet"},{"time":64295,"text":"and captured the whole scene on camera."},{"time":69057,"text":"It shows Captain Swenson and his comrade"},{"time":72263,"text":"bringing this wounded soldier"},{"time":73489,"text":"who had received a gunshot to the neck."},{"time":78039,"text":"They put him in the helicopter,"},{"time":81532,"text":"and then you see Captain Swenson bend over"},{"time":85860,"text":"and give him a kiss"},{"time":88043,"text":"before he turns around to rescue more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92881,"text":"I saw this, and I thought to myself,"},{"time":96088,"text":"where do people like that come from?"},{"time":98860,"text":"What is that? That is some deep, deep emotion,"},{"time":101903,"text":"when you would want to do that."},{"time":103604,"text":"There's a love there,"},{"time":105644,"text":"and I wanted to know why is it that"},{"time":107778,"text":"I don't have people that I work with like that?"},{"time":110462,"text":"You know, in the military, they give medals"},{"time":111880,"text":"to people who are willing to sacrifice themselves"},{"time":114502,"text":"so that others may gain."},{"time":116340,"text":"In business, we give bonuses to people"},{"time":118268,"text":"who are willing to sacrifice others"},{"time":119976,"text":"so that we may gain."},{"time":121470,"text":"We have it backwards. Right?"},{"time":125134,"text":"So I asked myself, where do\npeople like this come from?"},{"time":127013,"text":"And my initial conclusion was\nthat they're just better people."},{"time":130236,"text":"That's why they're attracted to the military."},{"time":131756,"text":"These better people are attracted"},{"time":133217,"text":"to this concept of service."},{"time":135963,"text":"But that's completely wrong."},{"time":137063,"text":"What I learned was that it's the environment,"},{"time":139900,"text":"and if you get the environment right,"},{"time":142070,"text":"every single one of us has the capacity"},{"time":143793,"text":"to do these remarkable things,"},{"time":145311,"text":"and more importantly, others have that capacity too."},{"time":148142,"text":"I've had the great honor of getting to meet"},{"time":150587,"text":"some of these, who we would call heroes,"},{"time":153702,"text":"who have put themselves and put their lives"},{"time":155604,"text":"at risk to save others,"},{"time":157203,"text":"and I asked them, \"Why would you do it?"},{"time":159706,"text":"Why did you do it?\""},{"time":161759,"text":"And they all say the same thing:"},{"time":164660,"text":"\"Because they would have done it for me.\""},{"time":166760,"text":"It's this deep sense of trust and cooperation."},{"time":169667,"text":"So trust and cooperation are really important here."},{"time":172266,"text":"The problem with concepts of trust and cooperation"},{"time":175425,"text":"is that they are feelings, they are not instructions."},{"time":177730,"text":"I can't simply say to you, \"Trust me,\" and you will."},{"time":180765,"text":"I can't simply instruct two people \nto cooperate, and they will."},{"time":184000,"text":"It's not how it works. It's a feeling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186434,"text":"So where does that feeling come from?"},{"time":188848,"text":"If you go back 50,000 years"},{"time":190930,"text":"to the Paleolithic era,"},{"time":192109,"text":"to the early days of Homo sapiens,"},{"time":194265,"text":"what we find is that the world"},{"time":195880,"text":"was filled with danger,"},{"time":198215,"text":"all of these forces working very, very hard to kill us."},{"time":202607,"text":"Nothing personal."},{"time":204106,"text":"Whether it was the weather,"},{"time":206548,"text":"lack of resources,"},{"time":208188,"text":"maybe a saber-toothed tiger,"},{"time":209670,"text":"all of these things working"},{"time":211005,"text":"to reduce our lifespan."},{"time":213141,"text":"And so we evolved into social animals,"},{"time":215442,"text":"where we lived together and worked together"},{"time":217417,"text":"in what I call a circle of safety, inside the tribe,"},{"time":220841,"text":"where we felt like we belonged."},{"time":222864,"text":"And when we felt safe amongst our own,"},{"time":225595,"text":"the natural reaction was trust and cooperation."},{"time":228803,"text":"There are inherent benefits to this."},{"time":229905,"text":"It means I can fall asleep at night"},{"time":231793,"text":"and trust that someone from within\nmy tribe will watch for danger."},{"time":235665,"text":"If we don't trust each other, if I don't trust you,"},{"time":237997,"text":"that means you won't watch for danger."},{"time":239381,"text":"Bad system of survival."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241252,"text":"The modern day is exactly the same thing."},{"time":243591,"text":"The world is filled with danger,"},{"time":245212,"text":"things that are trying to frustrate our lives"},{"time":246967,"text":"or reduce our success,"},{"time":248136,"text":"reduce our opportunity for success."},{"time":249860,"text":"It could be the ups and downs in the economy,"},{"time":252229,"text":"the uncertainty of the stock market."},{"time":254569,"text":"It could be a new technology that renders"},{"time":256313,"text":"your business model obsolete overnight."},{"time":258470,"text":"Or it could be your competition"},{"time":260119,"text":"that is sometimes trying to kill you."},{"time":262119,"text":"It's sometimes trying to put you out of business,"},{"time":264004,"text":"but at the very minimum"},{"time":265715,"text":"is working hard to frustrate your growth"},{"time":268378,"text":"and steal your business from you."},{"time":270508,"text":"We have no control over these forces."},{"time":272253,"text":"These are a constant,"},{"time":273770,"text":"and they're not going away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275748,"text":"The only variable are the conditions"},{"time":277794,"text":"inside the organization,"},{"time":280357,"text":"and that's where leadership matters,"},{"time":282282,"text":"because it's the leader that sets the tone."},{"time":284961,"text":"When a leader makes the choice"},{"time":287400,"text":"to put the safety and lives"},{"time":288929,"text":"of the people inside the organization first,"},{"time":291190,"text":"to sacrifice their comforts and sacrifice"},{"time":294068,"text":"the tangible results, so that the people remain"},{"time":297573,"text":"and feel safe and feel like they belong,"},{"time":299000,"text":"remarkable things happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301894,"text":"I was flying on a trip,"},{"time":305013,"text":"and I was witness to an incident"},{"time":307128,"text":"where a passenger attempted to board"},{"time":309016,"text":"before their number was called,"},{"time":312627,"text":"and I watched the gate agent"},{"time":315196,"text":"treat this man like he had broken the law,"},{"time":317620,"text":"like a criminal."},{"time":319029,"text":"He was yelled at for attempting to board"},{"time":320875,"text":"one group too soon."},{"time":323246,"text":"So I said something."},{"time":324690,"text":"I said, \"Why do you have treat us like cattle?"},{"time":327360,"text":"Why can't you treat us like human beings?\""},{"time":330451,"text":"And this is exactly what she said to me."},{"time":332572,"text":"She said, \"Sir, if I don't follow the rules,"},{"time":335258,"text":"I could get in trouble or lose my job.\""},{"time":338408,"text":"All she was telling me"},{"time":339990,"text":"is that she doesn't feel safe."},{"time":341646,"text":"All she was telling me is that"},{"time":343987,"text":"she doesn't trust her leaders."},{"time":347206,"text":"The reason we like flying Southwest Airlines"},{"time":349928,"text":"is not because they necessarily hire better people."},{"time":352395,"text":"It's because they don't fear their leaders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355434,"text":"You see, if the conditions are wrong,"},{"time":357356,"text":"we are forced to expend our own time and energy"},{"time":359615,"text":"to protect ourselves from each other,"},{"time":362479,"text":"and that inherently weakens the organization."},{"time":365778,"text":"When we feel safe inside the organization,"},{"time":367409,"text":"we will naturally combine our talents"},{"time":369603,"text":"and our strengths and work tirelessly"},{"time":371749,"text":"to face the dangers outside"},{"time":373431,"text":"and seize the opportunities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376566,"text":"The closest analogy I can give"},{"time":377887,"text":"to what a great leader is, is like being a parent."},{"time":381099,"text":"If you think about what being a great parent is,"},{"time":382758,"text":"what do you want? What makes a great parent?"},{"time":384588,"text":"We want to give our child opportunities,"},{"time":385940,"text":"education, discipline them when necessary,"},{"time":388658,"text":"all so that they can grow up and achieve more"},{"time":390694,"text":"than we could for ourselves."},{"time":393259,"text":"Great leaders want exactly the same thing."},{"time":395000,"text":"They want to provide their people opportunity,"},{"time":396501,"text":"education, discipline when necessary,"},{"time":398288,"text":"build their self-confidence, give\nthem the opportunity to try and fail,"},{"time":401450,"text":"all so that they could achieve more"},{"time":403161,"text":"than we could ever imagine for ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407591,"text":"Charlie Kim, who's the CEO of\na company called Next Jump"},{"time":410728,"text":"in New York City, a tech company,"},{"time":413478,"text":"he makes the point that"},{"time":414970,"text":"if you had hard times in your family,"},{"time":417099,"text":"would you ever consider laying\noff one of your children?"},{"time":420148,"text":"We would never do it."},{"time":421650,"text":"Then why do we consider laying off people"},{"time":423677,"text":"inside our organization?"},{"time":425254,"text":"Charlie implemented a policy"},{"time":428054,"text":"of lifetime employment."},{"time":429990,"text":"If you get a job at Next Jump,"},{"time":431620,"text":"you cannot get fired for performance issues."},{"time":435080,"text":"In fact, if you have issues,"},{"time":437063,"text":"they will coach you and they will give you support,"},{"time":440110,"text":"just like we would with one of our children"},{"time":441571,"text":"who happens to come home with a C from school."},{"time":444410,"text":"It's the complete opposite."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445363,"text":"This is the reason so many people"},{"time":446980,"text":"have such a visceral hatred, anger,"},{"time":451244,"text":"at some of these banking CEOs"},{"time":452912,"text":"with their disproportionate\nsalaries and bonus structures."},{"time":455740,"text":"It's not the numbers."},{"time":457710,"text":"It's that they have violated the\nvery definition of leadership."},{"time":460548,"text":"They have violated this deep-seated social contract."},{"time":463442,"text":"We know that they allowed their people"},{"time":465045,"text":"to be sacrificed so they could\nprotect their own interests,"},{"time":467560,"text":"or worse, they sacrificed their people"},{"time":470752,"text":"to protect their own interests."},{"time":472212,"text":"This is what so offends us, not the numbers."},{"time":475023,"text":"Would anybody be offended if we gave"},{"time":476620,"text":"a $150 million bonus to Gandhi?"},{"time":479193,"text":"How about a $250 million bonus to Mother Teresa?"},{"time":482232,"text":"Do we have an issue with that? None at all."},{"time":484966,"text":"None at all."},{"time":486298,"text":"Great leaders would never sacrifice"},{"time":488509,"text":"the people to save the numbers."},{"time":489870,"text":"They would sooner sacrifice the numbers"},{"time":491549,"text":"to save the people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494528,"text":"Bob Chapman, who runs"},{"time":496651,"text":"a large manufacturing company in the Midwest"},{"time":498964,"text":"called Barry-Wehmiller,"},{"time":501040,"text":"in 2008 was hit very hard by the recession,"},{"time":506397,"text":"and they lost 30 percent of their orders overnight."},{"time":510398,"text":"Now in a large manufacturing company,"},{"time":511784,"text":"this is a big deal,"},{"time":513325,"text":"and they could no longer afford their labor pool."},{"time":516172,"text":"They needed to save 10 million dollars,"},{"time":517875,"text":"so, like so many companies today,"},{"time":519898,"text":"the board got together and discussed layoffs."},{"time":523292,"text":"And Bob refused."},{"time":524916,"text":"You see, Bob doesn't believe in head counts."},{"time":529168,"text":"Bob believes in heart counts,"},{"time":532609,"text":"and it's much more difficult to simply reduce"},{"time":535117,"text":"the heart count."},{"time":536847,"text":"And so they came up with a furlough program."},{"time":539854,"text":"Every employee, from secretary to CEO,"},{"time":541945,"text":"was required to take four weeks of unpaid vacation."},{"time":545411,"text":"They could take it any time they wanted,"},{"time":547322,"text":"and they did not have to take it consecutively."},{"time":550303,"text":"But it was how Bob announced the program"},{"time":551635,"text":"that mattered so much."},{"time":553532,"text":"He said, it's better that we should all suffer a little"},{"time":556180,"text":"than any of us should have to suffer a lot,"},{"time":558965,"text":"and morale went up."},{"time":562083,"text":"They saved 20 million dollars,"},{"time":565010,"text":"and most importantly, as would be expected,"},{"time":567447,"text":"when the people feel safe and protected\nby the leadership in the organization,"},{"time":570676,"text":"the natural reaction is to trust and cooperate."},{"time":573183,"text":"And quite spontaneously, nobody expected,"},{"time":575940,"text":"people started trading with each other."},{"time":577856,"text":"Those who could afford it more"},{"time":579352,"text":"would trade with those who could afford it less."},{"time":581429,"text":"People would take five weeks"},{"time":582918,"text":"so that somebody else only had to take three."}]},{"cues":[{"time":587080,"text":"Leadership is a choice. It is not a rank."},{"time":590014,"text":"I know many people at the seniormost"},{"time":591722,"text":"levels of organizations"},{"time":592880,"text":"who are absolutely not leaders."},{"time":594484,"text":"They are authorities, and we do what they say"},{"time":597037,"text":"because they have authority over us,"},{"time":600080,"text":"but we would not follow them."},{"time":601940,"text":"And I know many people"},{"time":603974,"text":"who are at the bottoms of organizations"},{"time":605336,"text":"who have no authority"},{"time":606599,"text":"and they are absolutely leaders,"},{"time":608662,"text":"and this is because they have chosen to look after"},{"time":610447,"text":"the person to the left of them,"},{"time":611965,"text":"and they have chosen to look after"},{"time":613243,"text":"the person to the right of them."},{"time":615037,"text":"This is what a leader is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619770,"text":"I heard a story"},{"time":622800,"text":"of some Marines"},{"time":624390,"text":"who were out in theater,"},{"time":627711,"text":"and as is the Marine custom,"},{"time":629757,"text":"the officer ate last,"},{"time":632082,"text":"and he let his men eat first,"},{"time":635258,"text":"and when they were done,"},{"time":637110,"text":"there was no food left for him."},{"time":641200,"text":"And when they went back out in the field,"},{"time":643933,"text":"his men brought him some of their food"},{"time":646877,"text":"so that he may eat,"},{"time":648734,"text":"because that's what happens."},{"time":650873,"text":"We call them leaders because they go first."},{"time":653562,"text":"We call them leaders because they take the risk"},{"time":655305,"text":"before anybody else does."},{"time":656960,"text":"We call them leaders because they will choose"},{"time":658990,"text":"to sacrifice so that their people"},{"time":660999,"text":"may be safe and protected"},{"time":662118,"text":"and so their people may gain,"},{"time":664254,"text":"and when we do, the natural response"},{"time":667308,"text":"is that our people will sacrifice for us."},{"time":671155,"text":"They will give us their blood and sweat and tears"},{"time":673653,"text":"to see that their leader's vision comes to life,"},{"time":677092,"text":"and when we ask them, \"Why would you do that?"},{"time":679864,"text":"Why would you give your blood and sweat and tears"},{"time":682251,"text":"for that person?\" they all say the same thing:"},{"time":686735,"text":"\"Because they would have done it for me.\""},{"time":689233,"text":"And isn't that the organization"},{"time":691383,"text":"we would all like to work in?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":693704,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":696261,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":699862,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}